nodes.text: David Whitehall is an English actor who appeared as an extra in Rogue One: A Star Wars Story and played a Casino Customer in Star Wars: Episode VIII The Last Jedi. He was originally set to play Willow Ufgood in the 1988 film Willow before losing out to Warwick Davis.
